Graven Effigy.description:
Drop a |cffffffffGraven Effigy|r near you for 1 min.

Enemies within 20 yds have the duration of crowd control effects on them increased by 25%.

@ext:Can only have 1 |cffffffffEffigy|r active at a time.:ext@

Mojo Beam.description:
Bring mojo to an ally, healing for 223 every 1 sec for 4 sec. 

While channeling, you can instantly cast |cFFFFFFFFPotion Toss|r, |cFFFFFFFFSplash Potion|r and |cFFFFFFFFSpirit in a Bottle|r at a 20% increased cost.

@ext:This spell is unaffected by haste modifiers.:ext@

Shadow Effigy.description:
Drop a |cffffffffShadow Effigy|r near you for 1 min.

Enemies within 30 yds have their casting speed reduced by 20% and movement speed by 40%.

@ext:Can only have 1 |cffffffffEffigy|r active at a time.:ext@

Stasis Ward.description:
Drop a |cffffffffStasis Ward|r near you.

After 2 sec, the ward will burst with lightning, stunning nearby enemies for 4 sec and dealing 12 Nature damage.

@ext:Can only have 1 |cffffffffWard|r active at a time.:ext@
